"{\"uid\": \"wishtv.com-news-local-news-celebrating-fathers-day-at-the-us-olympic-swim-trials\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"INDIANAPOLIS (WISH) - Sunday marks the second day of the U.S. Olympic Swim Trials at Lucas Oil Stadium, along with Father's Day.Dads and their kids flocked from all over the state, along with Canada, to celebrate both occasions, something they likely will not get the opportunity to do again.Soon-to-be eighth grader Canon Swinehart, from Warsaw, says his family often spends their Father's Days \\\"sitting around the house.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.8817954581209525, \"rank\": 0.09534675453384395, \"text\": \"INDIANAPOLIS\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.772867728501165e-17, \"text\": \"WISH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999652578586207, \"rank\": 2.3748842256664404e-05, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warsaw\", \"score\": 0.9960699352101404, \"rank\": 0.00394552939551903, \"text\": \"Warsaw\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warsaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warsaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This year, though, he and his older brother, Calin Swinehart, got the chance to travel to downtown Indianapolis for the first time with their dad to witness the U.S. Olympic